1
00:00:08,600 --> 00:00:10,160
Xiaochao.

2
00:00:24,280 --> 00:00:25,200
Xiaochao.

3
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:27,000
Don't leave me behind.

4
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:34,979
Ah Fu, do you remember this place?

5
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:36,620
I remember.

6
00:01:41,479 --> 00:01:42,200
Eat.

7
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:43,600
Thanks.

8
00:01:44,759 --> 00:01:45,759
I remember.

9
00:01:45,759 --> 00:01:48,560
You were the one who brought me here the first time.

10
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:50,600
Back then,

11
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:51,840
whenever we skipped class,

12
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,770
we'd come here to eat rice noodles.

13
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:55,160
Boss, I was wrong.

14
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:57,320
I shouldn't have been hiding from you.

15
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:58,240
You told me to keep an eye on Zhang Chao,

16
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,570
I've been watching him.

17
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:00,640
Alright, alright.

18
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,240
Even when I go to the bathroom, I keep an eye on him.

19
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,170
Alright, I know.

20
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:04,680
Don't think about this anymore.

21
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:05,720
Eat your noodles.

22
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,039
Boss, you don't blame me?

23
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:09,520
Two scoops, I remember.

24
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,320
Right?

25
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:14,640
Two scoops.

26
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,160
I only want one scoop.

27
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,680
Eat up.

28
00:02:21,320 --> 00:02:22,920
So what should I do now?

29
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,000
Ah Fu,

30
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,800
do you remember

31
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,160
how we first met?

32
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,520
I remember.

33
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:36,600
That day,

34
00:02:37,720 --> 00:02:40,720
I was waiting for my dad to pick me up at the school gate.

35
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,880
When is your mom coming?

36
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:55,520
She'll be here in a bit.

37
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,650
My dad will definitely be here faster.

38
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:16,040
Xu Ah Fu,

39
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:17,520
want to come over to my house to play?

40
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,520
No way.

41
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,920
I want to go home and play video games.

42
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:21,850
I don't want to study math with you.

43
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,360
I have a video game console too.

44
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,560
Imported from Japan.

45
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:25,880
Imported?

46
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:27,000
Do you have Mario?

47
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,800
I have Contra, Final Fantasy,

48
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:29,600
and Digimon.

49
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:31,530
What are you waiting for? Let's go.

50
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:40,400
Eat a big chicken leg.

51
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,130
Thanks, Dad.

52
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,680
What are you so happy about?

53
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,480
Dad, I made a good brother.

54
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,240
Really?

55
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:55,920
Really.

56
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:59,200
I suddenly realized,

57
00:03:59,200 --> 00:03:59,800
you

58
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:02,240
are just like me when I was young.

59
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:02,800
Here,

60
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,720
have another chicken leg.

61
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:04,120
Here.

62
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:06,440
Thanks, Dad.

63
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:09,360
Since then, I made up my mind.

64
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,160
I'll always follow you.

65
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,560
You are my boss.

66
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,399
Ah Fu,

67
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:17,480
do you envy me?

68
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,839
Envy you?

69
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,440
Many people envy me.

70
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,970
Envy me for having luxury cars,

71
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:28,200
beautiful women,

72
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:30,200
endless money.

73
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:33,060
They envy me even more because my dad is Lin Yongtai.

74
00:04:33,520 --> 00:04:34,800
But you know what?

75
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,960
Sometimes I really envy you.

76
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,760
Envy me?

77
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:41,060
What's there to envy about me?

78
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:42,960
I envy you

79
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:45,220
for having a father who understands you.

80
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:46,560
I envy you.

81
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:49,920
So I could be happy

82
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,520
and live a carefree life.

83
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:56,360
It's all my fault.

84
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:59,560
How did I get into such big trouble?

85
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,970
Let me tell you about my childhood.

86
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,000
Ever since I was little,

87
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,460
whenever I made a mistake,

88
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:09,440
my dad would lock me in a dark room.

89
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:12,120
Sometimes for a whole week.

90
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,480
I'd scream my lungs out,

91
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,120
and no matter how hard I knocked on the door,

92
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:18,000
no one dared to open it for me.

93
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:22,960
Ah Fu,

94
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:25,140
stop following me.

95
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:25,960
No, just...

96
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:26,720
Hear me out.

97
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:29,800
At the very least,

98
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:32,580
I have my dad behind me.

99
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:35,490
Trust me.

100
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:36,640
No.

101
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:46,720
Boss.

102
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:18,240
Ah Fu.

103
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:20,700
Stop following me.

104
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:29,360
Dad.

105
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,120
Dad.

106
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,680
Are you asleep?

107
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,360
Don't go to sleep just yet.

108
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,760
Let me ask you a question.

109
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,720
What question?

110
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:44,020
If your friend made a mistake,

111
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,500
would you help him?

112
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:48,840
It depends on what kind of friend.

113
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:51,080
The kind

114
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,140
that is very close,

115
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,760
like a real brother.

116
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,520
Of course.

117
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:06,840
Let me tell you,

118
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,580
when it comes to brothers,

119
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:10,560
if they treat you half well,

120
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,440
you must

121
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,440
repay them fully.

122
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:16,200
For a brother,

123
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:18,520
you can lose your head

124
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,240
and shed your blood.

125
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,960
If there is a fortune,

126
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,640
you make it together.

127
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,600
If there is

128
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,640
a huge mistake,

129
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,920
you bear it together.

130
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:30,640
Hear me?

131
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:34,120
I get it, I get it.

132
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,240
Go to sleep.

133
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:37,200
That's right. That's right.

134
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:38,760
You should change your bed soon.

135
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:40,159
It's creaking.

136
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:54,320
Boss.

137
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:57,040
We are brothers.

138
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:59,680
I started this.

139
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:02,120
Let me take the blame for you.

140
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,840
Hello, everyone.

141
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:39,120
I am Li Weihao's classmate, Xu Afu.

142
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:46,320
I admit to the fact that I bullied Li Weihao.

143
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:54,080
I was the one who made him kneel on the ground and act like a dog.

144
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:55,880
The one who bullied him

145
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:57,940
and made him serve others was also me.

146
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,680
I did it all.

147
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:03,740
It has nothing to do with anyone else.

148
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,080
Don't you know how to dodge?

149
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,400
I shouldn't have built my happiness

150
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:10,200
on the suffering of others.

151
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,800
Do you even know how to dodge?

152
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,200
It's trying to eat you, you know?

153
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,560
Why didn't you dodge?

154
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:17,000
I...

155
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:19,060
Li Weihao's departure

156
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:22,240
made me deeply realize my mistakes.

157
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:24,560
Can't you see it's trying to eat you?

158
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:25,640
I...

159
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:28,120
I want to apologize

160
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:30,200
to Li Weihao's family.

161
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:33,840
I sincerely ask for

162
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:36,600
Li Weihao's family's forgiveness.

163
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:47,610
And I also ask for

164
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,160
the teachers'

165
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:51,570
and classmates' forgiveness.

166
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:53,360
I'm sorry.

167
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:34,880
I admit that I bullied Li Weihao.

168
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:05,760
Guixiang.

169
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:08,280
Guixiang.

170
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:11,770
I was the one who made him serve others.

171
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:13,000
I did it all.

172
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:15,260
It has nothing to do with anyone else.

173
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:18,080
I want to apologize to Li Weihao.

174
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:20,040
I shouldn't build my own happiness

175
00:11:20,040 --> 00:11:21,840
on the suffering of others.

176
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,440
Oh no.

177
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:30,690
Wenyu 10752.

178
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:45,760
Ms. Chen,

179
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,440
why are you here?

180
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:50,520
What's going on with those photos?

181
00:11:50,520 --> 00:11:51,440
What photos?

182
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,920
You mean the foundation photos?

183
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:54,880
Didn't I explain that already?

184
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:56,210
Zhang Chao posted them.

185
00:11:56,520 --> 00:11:57,800
You still won't admit it.

186
00:11:57,800 --> 00:12:00,060
I'm asking about what's in those photos!

187
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:02,000
We just went out

188
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,080
and took some random photos.

189
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:03,920
It's normal for friends to fool around.

190
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:04,840
You hit my son!

191
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:08,400
Ma'am, ma'am, ma'am,

192
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:09,960
please calm down.

193
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:12,080
Went out to play?

194
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:12,640
Ma'am!

195
00:12:12,640 --> 00:12:13,080
I'll show you 'going out to play'!

196
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:13,920
Ms. Chen!

197
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:15,280
Ma'am!

198
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:16,360
Stop her!

199
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:17,000
Ma'am!

200
00:12:17,560 --> 00:12:18,920
I'll let you play!

201
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:19,840
Guixiang!

202
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:21,680
Your wife is crazy!

203
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:22,520
Get lost!

204
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:23,640
Stop!

205
00:12:23,640 --> 00:12:24,960
Guixiang! Ah Fu!

206
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:26,240
The knife!

207
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:27,520
Guixiang! Ah Fu! Guixiang! Guixiang!

208
00:12:27,520 --> 00:12:28,840
The knife!

209
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:30,120
Don't stop me!

210
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,480
Put the knife down!

211
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:32,970
What's going on?

212
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:34,560
Calm down!

213
00:12:34,560 --> 00:12:35,920
Put the knife down!

214
00:12:35,920 --> 00:12:39,800
Put it down! Let go of me!

215
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:40,560
Guixiang! Guixiang!

216
00:12:40,560 --> 00:12:41,320
Guixiang, that's enough.

217
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:42,560
We can't do anything stupid.

218
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:43,760
Calm down! Calm down!

219
00:12:43,760 --> 00:12:45,240
I want to avenge my son!

220
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:47,320
I want to avenge my son! Calm down!

221
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:48,560
Guixiang! I want to avenge my son!

222
00:12:48,560 --> 00:12:50,120
Guixiang, calm down!

223
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:52,120
Calm down!

224
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:52,800
Let go!

225
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:57,760
I was wrong.

226
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,120
Hit me.

227
00:13:06,560 --> 00:13:07,420
Let me tell you,

228
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:10,160
you'd better explain everything clearly today.

229
00:13:10,160 --> 00:13:11,290
If they bullied you,

230
00:13:11,560 --> 00:13:12,480
I will right now

231
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:14,160
go and fight them to the death.

232
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:15,740
With your dad here,

233
00:13:15,920 --> 00:13:17,320
you have nothing to fear.

234
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,200
But if you

235
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,080
made a mistake,

236
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:22,800
I won't let you off either.

237
00:13:22,800 --> 00:13:24,130
As Xu Changjiang's son,

238
00:13:24,280 --> 00:13:25,200
you take the beating if you're wrong.

239
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:26,480
If you're not wrong, you don't admit it.

240
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:27,360
If you did nothing wrong,

241
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:28,520
you must not admit to it.

242
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:29,250
Understand?

243
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,040
Alright.

244
00:13:31,040 --> 00:13:31,720
Tell me.

245
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:33,240
Who is that woman?

246
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:35,120
Why did she try to hack you with a knife?

247
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,720
She is Li Weihao's mother.

248
00:13:41,480 --> 00:13:43,540
Thank you. Have some water, Ms. Chen.

249
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:47,920
I'm really sorry.

250
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,520
My wife

251
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:51,360
did something stupid out of impulse

252
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,820
and caused you to get hurt.

253
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:54,080
It's fine.

254
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:55,540
What do you mean by stupid?

255
00:13:56,040 --> 00:13:57,560
The murderer was right there.

256
00:13:57,560 --> 00:13:59,280
Was I supposed to just watch

257
00:13:59,280 --> 00:14:00,920
and do nothing?

258
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:02,800
What else do you want?

259
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:04,760
You slashed someone with a knife.

260
00:14:04,760 --> 00:14:05,920
Ms. Chen is still hurt.

261
00:14:05,920 --> 00:14:07,800
Just calm down!

262
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:09,440
I'm fine. Don't blame her.

263
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:14,320
Anyone would lose it seeing that.

264
00:14:15,040 --> 00:14:16,520
Moreover,

265
00:14:16,520 --> 00:14:18,120
you are Weihao's parents.

266
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:20,320
She was emotional

267
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,860
because she loves Weihao so much.

268
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:24,040
Yes.

269
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:28,100
What parent in this world doesn't love their child?

270
00:14:29,240 --> 00:14:30,560
So that's how it is.

271
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:34,360
You mean to say,

272
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:35,980
you bullied their son?

273
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:37,040
Are

274
00:14:37,680 --> 00:14:38,320
you

275
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:39,440
right?

276
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:40,440
No.

277
00:14:41,280 --> 00:14:43,440
It was Lin Jiaming.

278
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,060
You're a huge jerk!

279
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:47,400
Lin Jiaming tells you to hit someone,

280
00:14:47,400 --> 00:14:48,400
and you actually do it?

281
00:14:48,400 --> 00:14:49,360
He tells you to take the blame,

282
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:50,280
and you take it?

283
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:51,760
If Lin Jiaming

284
00:14:51,760 --> 00:14:53,720
told you to slash your own father with a knife,

285
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:55,080
would you actually do it?

286
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:56,400
Didn't you teach me

287
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:57,600
that if a friend is somewhat good to you,

288
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:59,530
you should be twice as good to them?

289
00:15:00,120 --> 00:15:01,840
That's true,

290
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:03,320
but when you make friends,

291
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:05,050
you need to keep your eyes open!

292
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:08,120
You shouldn't treat all friends the same,

293
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:08,760
right?

294
00:15:08,760 --> 00:15:10,720
And not everyone deserves

295
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:11,920
your full sincerity.

296
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:13,440
That kind of relationship

297
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:16,200
is meant for real brothers, you know?

298
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:18,080
Lin Jiaming is my real brother.

299
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,360
He's been so good to me since we were kids.

300
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:20,240
He's in trouble.

301
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:21,440
How could I not save him?

302
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:22,970
I'll never trust you again.

303
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:23,940
Let me tell you,

304
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:24,960
that Lin Jiaming,

305
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:26,240
I've always felt

306
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:27,760
that he's up to no good.

307
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:30,280
What is a real brother?

308
00:15:30,280 --> 00:15:31,240
Do you know?

309
00:15:31,640 --> 00:15:33,240
When you do something wrong,

310
00:15:33,280 --> 00:15:34,080
a brother

311
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:35,800
will teach you how to be a better person,

312
00:15:35,800 --> 00:15:36,680
instead of making you

313
00:15:36,680 --> 00:15:37,960
more and more confused.

314
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,020
Do you understand?

315
00:15:41,040 --> 00:15:42,440
Getting involved in this

316
00:15:42,800 --> 00:15:45,280
will be a stain on you for life.

317
00:15:46,160 --> 00:15:47,960
Never mind Li Weihao's mother,

318
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:49,680
the school won't let you off either.

319
00:15:49,680 --> 00:15:50,280
Honestly,

320
00:15:50,280 --> 00:15:52,040
when you enter society,

321
00:15:52,040 --> 00:15:54,760
you'll have a hard time finding a decent job.

322
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:56,440
How will you survive in the future?

323
00:15:56,440 --> 00:15:57,520
Living off me.

324
00:15:57,960 --> 00:15:59,160
Don't worry, Dad.

325
00:15:59,160 --> 00:16:00,560
Lin Jiaming won't just ignore me.

326
00:16:00,560 --> 00:16:01,120
He's my boss.

327
00:16:01,120 --> 00:16:02,580
He'll definitely help me.

328
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:05,930
Will he look after you for your whole life?

329
00:16:06,280 --> 00:16:07,080
You,

330
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:08,360
seriously.

331
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:10,360
You don't know the pain

332
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:12,360
until the knife cuts your own flesh.

333
00:16:13,520 --> 00:16:14,720
Forget it.

334
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:16,160
You made this mess,

335
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:18,200
so you bear the consequences.

336
00:16:18,200 --> 00:16:18,880
Kneel down.

337
00:16:19,160 --> 00:16:19,920
Kneel.

338
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:24,920
Think it over carefully.

339
00:16:24,920 --> 00:16:27,450
Don't get up until you've thought it through.

340
00:16:30,560 --> 00:16:32,080
Why? Why?

341
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:41,040
I just don't understand.

342
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:42,880
You're saying my son

343
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:44,080
had depression,

344
00:16:44,480 --> 00:16:45,480
and was bullied

345
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:47,520
and tormented at school.

346
00:16:48,040 --> 00:16:49,880
We are his parents.

347
00:16:50,560 --> 00:16:52,280
Why didn't he tell us?

348
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:54,640
Why wouldn't he talk to us?

349
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:59,120
When many children face school bullying,

350
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:00,440
they are too young

351
00:17:01,040 --> 00:17:03,360
to even realize it is bullying.

352
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:05,400
They think

353
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:07,569
it will pass if they just endure it.

354
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:09,160
Weihao

355
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:12,040
is a kind boy,

356
00:17:12,599 --> 00:17:14,460
and he was afraid of worrying you.

357
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:19,599
Why was he

358
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:23,920
so silly?

359
00:17:27,119 --> 00:17:28,000
No.

360
00:17:29,240 --> 00:17:30,120
No.

361
00:17:30,360 --> 00:17:32,240
We are the silly ones.

362
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:33,800
All right.

363
00:17:34,520 --> 00:17:36,160
We are his parents.

364
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:37,960
It's been so many years.

365
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:42,280
Why didn't we notice anything?

366
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:43,760
Ma'am,

367
00:17:43,760 --> 00:17:45,890
please don't blame yourself too much.

368
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:47,440
I know

369
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,760
that within your abilities,

370
00:17:48,760 --> 00:17:50,960
you've already tried your best.

371
00:17:53,480 --> 00:17:54,920
It's just that a family

372
00:17:55,960 --> 00:17:57,640
has to deal with a lot.

373
00:17:58,080 --> 00:17:59,640
You also hear many voices.

374
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:01,880
It's inevitable that you

375
00:18:03,400 --> 00:18:05,200
would overlook Weihao's voice.

376
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:11,880
Dr. Chen.

377
00:18:12,520 --> 00:18:14,360
You are Weihao's therapist.

378
00:18:15,280 --> 00:18:17,210
You must know him very well, right?

379
00:18:17,280 --> 00:18:18,920
Did he say something to you?

380
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:21,360
Dr. Chen, can you tell me?

381
00:18:22,160 --> 00:18:22,960
Dr. Chen,

382
00:18:23,360 --> 00:18:23,920
I beg you.

383
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:25,480
Please tell me.

384
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:27,360
Dr. Chen,

385
00:18:27,360 --> 00:18:28,760
please tell me.

386
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:34,320
Since high school, Weihao

387
00:18:34,320 --> 00:18:35,980
started leaving me messages.

388
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:39,080
I've compiled some of his texts.

389
00:18:39,680 --> 00:18:40,760
Of course,

390
00:18:40,760 --> 00:18:42,960
these aren't exactly medical records.

391
00:18:43,320 --> 00:18:44,440
In my opinion,

392
00:18:45,080 --> 00:18:46,080
these are things

393
00:18:46,400 --> 00:18:47,960
he wanted to tell you,

394
00:18:48,520 --> 00:18:50,200
but never could.

395
00:18:51,360 --> 00:18:52,020
Take a look.

396
00:19:14,600 --> 00:19:15,280
Dr. Chen.

397
00:19:15,600 --> 00:19:17,260
Do you know what 'Abeibei' is?

398
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:18,800
You mean those

399
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:20,920
comfort objects for children?

400
00:19:21,240 --> 00:19:21,720
Yes.

401
00:19:22,240 --> 00:19:23,960
When I was little, I had an old pillow.

402
00:19:23,960 --> 00:19:25,480
My grandmother made it for me.

403
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:27,840
She passed away when I was very young.

404
00:19:27,840 --> 00:19:30,200
I don't even remember what she looked like.

405
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:32,480
But that pillow

406
00:19:32,480 --> 00:19:34,000
had been with me since I was born.

407
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:35,560
No matter what happened,

408
00:19:35,560 --> 00:19:37,000
as long as I held the corner of the pillow

409
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:38,200
and smelled its scent,

410
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:40,080
I would instantly feel completely safe. Xiaohao...

411
00:19:40,080 --> 00:19:41,920
Xiaohao, wake up for school.

412
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:44,840
Hurry up.

413
00:19:48,760 --> 00:19:50,040
Hurry.

414
00:19:50,040 --> 00:19:51,320
Stop dawdling.

415
00:20:09,800 --> 00:20:11,640
Mom.

416
00:20:12,560 --> 00:20:13,320
What is it?

417
00:20:13,320 --> 00:20:14,380
Where is my pillow?

418
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:16,840
Silly boy, isn't your pillow right here?

419
00:20:16,840 --> 00:20:17,520
Not this one.

420
00:20:17,520 --> 00:20:18,720
I mean my old one.

421
00:20:19,280 --> 00:20:20,480
I threw it away.

422
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:21,840
Where did you throw it?

423
00:20:21,840 --> 00:20:22,640
Where else?

424
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:24,040
The trash can.

425
00:20:24,040 --> 00:20:26,040
Why did you throw my things away?

426
00:20:26,800 --> 00:20:27,560
You child.

427
00:20:32,600 --> 00:20:33,840
Xiaohao, Xiaohao!

428
00:20:35,480 --> 00:20:37,320
Child, what are you doing here?

429
00:20:37,320 --> 00:20:38,360
It's so dirty.

430
00:20:38,360 --> 00:20:40,690
Why are you digging through the trash can?

431
00:20:43,040 --> 00:20:43,560
Alright, alright.

432
00:20:43,560 --> 00:20:44,160
Go back now.

433
00:20:44,160 --> 00:20:45,000
It's just a broken pillow.

434
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:46,240
What are you looking for?

435
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:48,120
I'm not going back! I'm not going back!

436
00:20:48,120 --> 00:20:49,760
Why did you throw my things away? Go back now!

437
00:20:49,760 --> 00:20:51,760
Why didn't you tell me? You're being difficult.

438
00:20:51,760 --> 00:20:52,600
Tell you what?

439
00:20:52,600 --> 00:20:53,520
Is that yours?

440
00:20:53,960 --> 00:20:55,440
What in this house is yours?

441
00:20:55,440 --> 00:20:56,240
Go back.

442
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:57,680
I'm not going back.

443
00:20:57,680 --> 00:20:58,600
You are so stubborn.

444
00:20:58,600 --> 00:21:00,000
Why do you want a broken pillow?

445
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:01,530
I love my parents very much.

446
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:03,800
I believe they love me too.

447
00:21:04,120 --> 00:21:06,160
But there are many things like this.

448
00:21:06,840 --> 00:21:08,560
They read my diary secretly.

449
00:21:08,560 --> 00:21:10,680
They stopped my favorite extracurricular classes.

450
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:12,920
They threw my little rabbit outside.

451
00:21:13,440 --> 00:21:15,400
They installed a security camera in my room.

452
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:18,240
They forced me to drink traditional Chinese medicine and milk.

453
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:20,000
In this house, I can't cry,

454
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:20,800
I can't get angry,

455
00:21:20,800 --> 00:21:22,000
I can't eat junk food,

456
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:23,360
I can't yell.

457
00:21:24,280 --> 00:21:25,920
I tried hard to be obedient

458
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:27,160
and accepting.

459
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:28,680
But even so,

460
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:30,040
in their eyes,

461
00:21:30,040 --> 00:21:31,880
I am still a weak

462
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:35,010
and useless person who can't do anything away from home.

463
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:41,840
Guixiang.

464
00:21:42,720 --> 00:21:44,650
You can't keep watching like this.

465
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:46,600
Weiguo.

466
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:49,640
Do you think Xiaohao got depression

467
00:21:50,080 --> 00:21:51,560
because of us?

468
00:21:51,560 --> 00:21:52,720
Impossible.

469
00:21:52,720 --> 00:21:53,600
Think about it.

470
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:55,600
We both love him so much.

471
00:21:56,560 --> 00:21:58,640
We love him so much that

472
00:21:59,160 --> 00:22:01,040
even when he left Qiongzhou

473
00:22:01,040 --> 00:22:02,800
to go to college in Beijing,

474
00:22:04,400 --> 00:22:05,880
I wouldn't let him.

475
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:18,720
Wrong again.

476
00:22:19,920 --> 00:22:21,000
Guixiang,

477
00:22:21,200 --> 00:22:22,680
guess what I just saw?

478
00:22:22,680 --> 00:22:23,400
What did you see?

479
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:25,200
Our son's college application form.

480
00:22:25,200 --> 00:22:26,720
Guess where he applied?

481
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:28,120
No need to guess.

482
00:22:28,120 --> 00:22:29,360
Qiongzhou University.

483
00:22:29,360 --> 00:22:30,720
I already picked a major for him.

484
00:22:30,720 --> 00:22:32,520
What Qiongzhou University?

485
00:22:32,760 --> 00:22:34,760
He applied to a university in Beijing.

486
00:22:34,760 --> 00:22:35,480
What?

487
00:22:36,280 --> 00:22:37,540
He's going to Beijing?

488
00:22:38,120 --> 00:22:39,840
Keep your voice down.

489
00:22:40,040 --> 00:22:41,770
What is he going to Beijing for?

490
00:22:43,080 --> 00:22:44,480
Exactly.

491
00:22:44,760 --> 00:22:46,560
Applying to college is such a big deal,

492
00:22:46,560 --> 00:22:47,880
and this child

493
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:49,920
made such a big decision on his own.

494
00:22:49,920 --> 00:22:51,780
He didn't even discuss it with us.

495
00:22:52,040 --> 00:22:53,840
Why does he want to go to Beijing?

496
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:56,720
A child who grew up in the south,

497
00:22:56,720 --> 00:22:57,800
why go to Beijing?

498
00:22:57,800 --> 00:22:59,080
Yes, it's the north.

499
00:22:59,080 --> 00:23:01,600
The lifestyle, food, and climate are all different.

500
00:23:01,600 --> 00:23:03,080
Will he get used to it?

501
00:23:04,120 --> 00:23:05,040
Besides,

502
00:23:06,000 --> 00:23:07,860
Qiongzhou is so far from Beijing.

503
00:23:08,000 --> 00:23:10,060
We'd hardly see him a few times a year.

504
00:23:10,120 --> 00:23:11,240
Exactly.

505
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:13,120
That's just for college.

506
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:15,440
If he gets a girlfriend later

507
00:23:15,440 --> 00:23:16,440
and stays in Beijing,

508
00:23:16,440 --> 00:23:18,700
we old folks will be completely left out.

509
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:20,560
No way.

510
00:23:20,560 --> 00:23:21,640
My son

511
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:23,280
must stay by my side.

512
00:23:24,560 --> 00:23:25,890
What are you going to do?

513
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:32,580
Has my admission letter arrived?

514
00:23:33,000 --> 00:23:34,600
Is it here? Has my admission letter arrived?

515
00:23:34,600 --> 00:23:35,560
It's here.

516
00:23:35,560 --> 00:23:37,000
It's here. Come quickly.

517
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:37,320
Hurry.

518
00:23:37,320 --> 00:23:38,120
I got in!

519
00:23:38,120 --> 00:23:39,320
Hurry and take a look.

520
00:23:47,840 --> 00:23:48,440
What the hell? This is it?

521
00:23:48,440 --> 00:23:49,040
Qiongzhou University?

522
00:23:49,040 --> 00:23:49,960
Is there a mistake?

523
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:51,600
What's wrong with Qiongzhou University?

524
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:53,160
It's the best university in Qiongzhou.

525
00:23:53,160 --> 00:23:54,040
It's nothing to be ashamed of.

526
00:23:54,040 --> 00:23:56,040
You've brought honor to our family.

527
00:23:56,040 --> 00:23:57,240
Not only brought honor,

528
00:23:57,240 --> 00:23:58,520
but more importantly, it's close to home.

529
00:23:58,520 --> 00:23:59,880
I can see my son every week.

530
00:23:59,880 --> 00:24:01,940
And I can cook delicious food for him.

531
00:24:02,560 --> 00:24:04,760
Did you change my application choices?

532
00:24:04,960 --> 00:24:06,760
Come on. Stop talking nonsense.

533
00:24:08,400 --> 00:24:08,960
It was you!

534
00:24:08,960 --> 00:24:09,960
I knew it was you!

535
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:13,040
Have I ever been allowed to make my own decisions since I was a kid?

536
00:24:13,040 --> 00:24:14,680
Haven't you decided everything for me?

537
00:24:14,680 --> 00:24:15,480
Why?

538
00:24:15,480 --> 00:24:17,280
You even had to change my university choices?

539
00:24:17,280 --> 00:24:18,680
Why? Because I am your mother!

540
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:20,440
He is your father! That's why!

541
00:24:20,440 --> 00:24:21,040
Alright.

542
00:24:21,040 --> 00:24:22,360
You are just a kid.

543
00:24:22,360 --> 00:24:25,400
Can you make such an important decision like going to college?

544
00:24:25,400 --> 00:24:26,160
Let me tell you,

545
00:24:26,160 --> 00:24:27,240
your mom didn't just randomly fill out

546
00:24:27,240 --> 00:24:28,360
your application choices.

547
00:24:28,360 --> 00:24:29,640
She consulted many experts

548
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:30,920
and looked up a lot of information.

549
00:24:30,920 --> 00:24:31,760
Look at you,

550
00:24:31,760 --> 00:24:32,600
instead of thanking your mom,

551
00:24:32,600 --> 00:24:34,360
you're yelling at her

552
00:24:34,360 --> 00:24:35,920
about the choices she checked.

553
00:24:35,920 --> 00:24:37,720
Is this the university I wanted to apply to?

554
00:24:37,720 --> 00:24:39,120
This is my life.

555
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:41,120
Have you ever respected me?

556
00:24:41,120 --> 00:24:42,800
Beijing is the city I want to go to.

557
00:24:42,800 --> 00:24:44,360
That is the major I want to study.

558
00:24:44,360 --> 00:24:45,680
But you just changed it.

559
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:47,120
Have you ever respected me?

560
00:24:47,120 --> 00:24:48,040
You asked everyone else.

561
00:24:48,040 --> 00:24:49,080
Did you ask me?

562
00:24:49,360 --> 00:24:50,320
I hate Qiongzhou.

563
00:24:50,320 --> 00:24:51,320
I hate this place.

564
00:24:51,320 --> 00:24:52,680
I hate you!

565
00:24:53,280 --> 00:24:54,080
You...

566
00:24:56,440 --> 00:24:57,840
What does he mean by this?

567
00:24:57,840 --> 00:24:58,970
What does this mean?

568
00:24:59,480 --> 00:25:00,640
Is he blaming me?

569
00:25:00,640 --> 00:25:01,520
Alright.

570
00:25:02,040 --> 00:25:03,960
Give him some time. He's still young.

571
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:05,160
He will figure it out.

572
00:25:25,080 --> 00:25:25,880
Xiaohao.

573
00:25:26,600 --> 00:25:27,600
Have some food.

574
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:30,080
Don't starve yourself.

575
00:25:31,040 --> 00:25:32,120
Xiaohao!

576
00:25:33,360 --> 00:25:34,560
He still won't eat?

577
00:25:36,400 --> 00:25:37,800
It's been days.

578
00:25:38,480 --> 00:25:40,160
Why is this kid so stubborn?

579
00:25:40,800 --> 00:25:42,200
I can tell now.

580
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:45,200
He doesn't really want to go to Beijing.

581
00:25:45,280 --> 00:25:46,760
He doesn't like this family.

582
00:25:46,760 --> 00:25:48,280
He doesn't like this mom anymore.

583
